content.p: Cripps Dental Centre provides NHS and private care for both staff and students. Our on-campus dental practice offers a range of treatments and preventative care. Cripps Dental Centre now has limited capacity to see Staff and their families as well as students of the University of Nottingham for routine care. Please contact our reception team. Cripps Dental Centre website To register at Cripps Dental Centre you will need to call 0115 950 6781 or 0115 951 3099. You'll find our dental centre at University Park, next to Cripps Health Centre Opening times There is limited parking available outside the practice. However, there is more parking a short walk away in our visitors' car park.
